[normal]cademy status.”
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“The inspection judgements and comments did not tell the school anything that they didn’t already know.  Comments as the inspectors left which stated they could see that the ethos of the school was outstanding as they entered the school, b
[normal]ut couldn’t comment on this, were not helpful in helping the school feel that inspection is broadly based and not just on data.”
